## Third-Party Attribution

This project reuses and rewrites the Weibo data-parsing logic (notably the
`parse_tweet_info` and `url_to_mid` functions and the AJAX endpoint usage)
from the open-source project:

    nghuyong/WeiboSpider
    https://github.com/nghuyong/WeiboSpider
    Licensed under the MIT License.

The original copyright and license of that project are acknowledged here in
accordance with the MIT License terms. This skill is an independent,
self-contained reimplementation focused on the lottery use case; it does not
bundle or depend on the upstream repository at runtime.
